benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/customFields/search/{searchKey} - Search custom fields

covered: GET Valid Request scenarios with 200 responses (TC01, TC02, TC03-05, TC07-09)
Query parameters variations (limit, offset, audit, extra params; TC10, TC11-14, TC28)
Default values and boundary tests (TC08, TC29, TC21/TC25/TC26)

Comprehensive empty-searchKey edge-case coverage across all conditions

recommendations: Add tests for rate limiting to ensure API handles bursts and enforces quotas

Add explicit 403 Forbidden authorization tests to complement 401 scenarios

Introduce sustained performance/load tests for prolonged concurrency and throughput beyond current scenarios
